      "text": "🔵 Blue = Mongoose Models\n🟣 Purple = TS Interfaces\n🟠 Orange = Controllers\n🟡 Yellow = Middleware\n🟢 Green = AI / Utilities\n🔴 Pink = React Components\n─── solid = composition\n- - - dashed = dependency\n···· dotted = HTTP call",
